Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the place?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Mansion 5055.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm finally here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You flipping {\i1}moron{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,College is so yesterday. Just quit it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the era of self-made men! {lit: era of actual/own talent now}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come work for me!\N We're currently seeking new staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Working in porn is great, man.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to see them for free, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.43,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa-senpai sounded\N so confident and assertive.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.64,0:02:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think I ditched college entrance exams to work at a porn video company...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If my mom heard about that, she'd probably get mad. {in the countryside}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Can I really? Can I?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so lewd!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.37,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What became of my innocent dream to become a world famous filmmaker, once so strong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd talk business with Coppola.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake hands with Spielberg!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Share a drink with Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.05,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream was to make movies \Ntogether with all those geniuses!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sexy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your papers...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.87,0:04:08.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Apollo Productions? But that's Ishikawa's porn film company.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that girl a porn star? No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am again.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No path in life is set in stone! {lit: there's no way life is a one track line [that you can's turn away from]}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a winding, thorny road... {connecting into previous line: [and I've now turned onto another road]}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.88,Top,,0,0,0,,Koganei Junpei, age 19!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.05,Top,,0,0,0,,It's a good time for an adventure! {show's title}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You're Koganei-san, here for the interview, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa-san told me a lot about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"A lot"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got quite a clean place.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.75,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the company staff are away now,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but they should be back soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,No bra!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? No, I mean... Pardon my curiosity, but who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.48,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I forgot to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.32,Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Wakaba Miwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.11,Top,,0,0,0,,I'm this company's exclusive porn star.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,this sweet looking girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,does {\i0}this{\i1} on camera...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,and {\i0}that{\i1}...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,A-And from that angle too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-san! You're too good!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're covered in sweat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.13,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koganei-san, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koganei-san, are you a virgin?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.39,0:06:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on. Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.48,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's more like... Yes.\N Does it show that much? I thought so.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Wakaba-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys mustn't be shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is going too far too quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's a big boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's pretty shy. How cute! {houkei-chan - houkei = phimosis and the condition leading up to it (abundant foreskin); here she likely means "but you're not circumcised [and by extension, he hides under the foreskin]" but Koganei mistakes it for the actual medical condition that requires medical intervention, hence the next 3 lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.01,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not right! Just let me roll it up.\NIt's a pseudo-phimosis! {true phi is the abnormal condition requiring medical intervention, pseudo-phi is a normal condition}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See? See?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strange guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you liked it. {lit: "received" - w/e that means}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.11,0:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm a very bad girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.64,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my love!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just your dick speaking! {lit: even though it's just dick - no idea what she means, maybe "I only meant your dick"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, I'm not afraid of the responsibility!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You just came here\N for an interview, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.92,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter! I don't care about that stupid interview!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.93,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"C-Cut?"
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,'sup, Koganei!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Ishikawa-senpai?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NWhat's going on? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.73,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your interview. This is the way we haze newcomers at Apollo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A-An interview? Is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Chief?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll make a good costar. \NWhat do you say? Did you like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.32,0:08:04.24,Top,,0,0,0,,Koganei, let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.79,Top,,0,0,0,,This is the company president, Ujiki-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.50,Top,,0,0,0,,And the cameraman, Ujitani-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.87,Top,,0,0,0,,You're a godsend. \NWe're always short on staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.87,Top,,0,0,0,,Our lighting designer, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.80,Top,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Foreskin-chan. {/uncircumcised/shy}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.84,Top,,0,0,0,,I'm the video engineer, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.84,0:08:24.72,Top,,0,0,0,,And this is our prodigy director, \NWakaba Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Director?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello and welcome to Apollo Productions.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we could try him out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei, I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.99,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just make the decision for me after dumping this joke of an interview on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't what you promised me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.91,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to audition as a porn actor!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you seemed pretty {\i1}into{\i0} it just now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... \NThat was that, and this...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I take that as a "yes." \NJust don't embarrass me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.68,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, for the newcomers, \Na lot of this stuff is brand new to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, we'll get\N the camera rolling, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.56,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting too ahead of yourself!\NEven I have a sense of honor!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I came from a small village in the north,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.47,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,determined to become a world-class filmmaker while holding my head high! {meaning "if I play in porn, I won't be able to hold my head high"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.66,0:09:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to look my family and friends in the eyes
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.10,0:09:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,after doing full frontal in a porn video?\N They had such high hopes for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already doing it! {lit: don't say in furuchin (having one's penis fully exposed (i.e. wearing no trousers or underwear)​) - likely means "don't say it while you're already full frontal/fully exposed"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You! The snot-faced boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you look down on us!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.51,0:09:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that porn videos \Nare the ultimate martial art of the senses!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.97,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some half-baked student experiment or a bland, lifeless commercial flick!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief, easy, easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's eat or be eaten!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.65,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who looks down on porn has no right \Nto make lofty claims about cinema!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't mind if I do! {/I will, gladly!}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.91,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey! Koganei!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you move it, jackass?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Kanekura!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.96,Top,,0,0,0,,Ujiki, I came for your answer. \NI'm sure you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.48,Top,,0,0,0,,No, just 20 more days...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please give us two more weeks!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have your interest by then!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to listen to excuses!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either to smash Apollo\N or settle it the {\i1}other{\i0} way. You choose. {not sure but I hear "do I crush appolo or take *that* option - it's one or another" probably the other option means something shady?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.07,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, we won't be able to film!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to scare you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Ujiki? It's in your hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Just give me two weeks!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A love hotel?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.87,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make me{, a girl,} say it twice. \NTo put it bluntly...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna do it with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! This is all so sudden!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.92,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no, Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in public!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.93,0:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't gonna end well!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind being watched.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to do it with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.61,0:12:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just a man and woman having sex. \NWe don't need an excuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wow. So this is what it looks like?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stare at it like that. \NJust do it already.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like these, we must shrug off our insecurities and shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, just a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a vivid dream it was!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.17,0:12:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She had such an innocent look \Nat the interview yesterday,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.55,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but she didn't even blush\N at the sight of my dick.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she's used to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably got a boyfriend,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe she'll still let me ravish her\N if I ask for it really hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.73,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My right hand! \NBeing young sucks! {右手が！若さが憎い！- "I hate youth" - idk what he means, probably that his sexual drive is unsurmountable}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna fuck Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna fuck her!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's better. {/I feel refreshed}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.33,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes? It's open! Come in!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa... Director Miwa!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Declaring your aspirations so loudly is a nuisance to your neighbors.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.17,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa-san gave me a map\N to where you live.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.68,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just really pushy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was about to give up on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,T-To what do I owe\N the pleasure of your visit? {lit: what do you want, so suddenly}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to bang me, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those gangsters yesterday must've scared you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose....
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an unusual occurrence in our line of work.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back. Eat up, Koganei-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.96,0:13:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, i-it's just that I'm so honored\N to go on a date with you, Director,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.84,0:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,b-but I'm not sure about being in a porno.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.55,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just out, eating hamburgers, is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had studied a little bit about film,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.85,0:14:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,although it was only 8mm films \Nat a rural film club.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.15,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I would love to be on the Apollo staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll do anything to help you, Director!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you'll do anything for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.46,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd like you to appear in my next film.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.54,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Apollo Productions will probably go under if our next project fails.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.38,0:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike mainstream cinema, indie films constantly struggle with tight budgets.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With budgets {\i1}and{\i0} talent.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.39,0:14:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to really communicate a moving experience,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,planning, execution, \Nand acting must be good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And more than anything, we need to come up\N with new characters constantly.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.28,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I should probably stop complaining.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.28,0:15:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be telling you this, \Nbut when we were really strapped for cash,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the Chief went to the man called \N"The Shadow King of the Industry."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how he ended up \Nin debt to Kanekura.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, he can buy all our new works for cheap, and he gets to meddle with production too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.49,0:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have to...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to get to you? {lit: he [did something] to you?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That lecherous old fart
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.75,0:15:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is pressuring our president to make a secret film for him, starring him and me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, he was counting
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on our new project, "Love Juice Angel,"\N starring Shinohara Chie, {arousal fluid; genital secretions; sexual fluids; love juice​}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.90,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to be our next big hit and help pay off the debt to Kanekura before he comes to collect.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! {\i1}The{\i0} Shinohara Chie?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.49,0:15:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She agreed to be paid afterward,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but in exchange, we gotta find her a costar to her liking.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you, it hit me hard \Nthat you'd fit that role perfectly. {to come (home) to one; to click; to ring a bell; to understand at once; to know intuitively; to get (a joke or explanation); to catch on​}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hitting me hard too. {self-explanatory}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a huge fan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.46,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it'll save you from your predicament, \NI will bang Chie-san with all my might!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Koganei-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, could you stop calling me "Koganei-kun"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Junpei.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.31,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Walking like this m-makes us\N look like lovers, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.78,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go somewhere lovers go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean this hotel?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. To scope out the location.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going in?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we are.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This next film mostly takes place in a love hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This room fits my image perfectly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's turn on the video.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, I can't hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't! A director mustn't get involved with an {apprentice }assistant!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get involved as man and woman!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great view, babe.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can totally see all the dirty stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in resisting!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your idea to come here, \Nso it's all consensual!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop! I had no idea\N you were that kind of person!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.04,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your own fault for going\N to this kind of place with a guy, babe.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You had it coming all along!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not what I had in mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fuck you up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you having that much fun \Nmumbling to the video?  {meaning he was voicing what just happened himself}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since we're already here, \Nlet's make use of the facilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.06,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you put this on?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.70,0:17:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your perception is too dull if you only realized it now. Call me "Queen"!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry more!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my {\i1}dog{\i0\fscx20} {\r}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I stooped too low! {lit: falling/to decline (of morals, character, etc.); to become vulgar (e.g. of a conversation); to stoop (to); to sink (so low)​}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really gonna do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Miwa-san, untie me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san! Do you really\N distrust me so much?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.43,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the guy screaming from inside his apartment that he wanted to bang me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.81,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I already paid for the room, so I might as well use the shower, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is torture!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.97,Top,,0,0,0,,Shinohara-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.81,0:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Junpei-kun! \NShe liked the script, and she liked you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm feeling kinda strung out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.27,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}When push comes to shove, you're the type\N who can transform completely to fit the role.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.87,0:19:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's move on to the flashback scene!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are we doing it for real in this take?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.71,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that maybe \Nwe can't do it without love involved.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Junpei-kun?\NYou can't get hard?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.76,0:19:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Junpei-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.81,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have sex with another woman \Nwhile the girl I like is watching!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.56,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't bring myself to say it. \NI guess she will end up...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go. Start the VTR.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The camera's rolling.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,5...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,4...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.74,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta pee!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.78,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too slow!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei! What'cha doing in there?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're calling from {\i1}where{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.71,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your "Sorry" going to help?! \NCome back here at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! {lit: under what conditions}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.67,0:20:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry... Is Miwa-san there?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't put her on the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in love with Director Wakaba?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't give up your virginity \Nin front of the woman you love?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake {\i1}up{\i0}, you dumdum!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck my life. {it's the worst}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.61,0:21:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, we've already started filming.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't undo the work of all these people.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.04,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's clear to me now.\NI misjudged you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.67,0:21:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.01,0:21:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Phone booth at the intersection with Street Two.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.68,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pathetic wimp! \NI had no idea he was like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, what should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.35,0:21:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be gentle with him, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your future husband, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.32,0:22:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!\NIt's not the time for jokes! {lit: fine! don't poke fun at me - but idk what she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.82,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was stood up.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.09,0:22:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.05,0:22:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.93,0:22:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.14,0:22:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got clothes for you in the car.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.15,0:22:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... We're going the opposite direction of the hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we are.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.41,0:22:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get any work done today.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.91,0:22:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.49,0:22:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You even brought your director to tears.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.37,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls simply don't know how to handle\N such a sudden and awkward confession.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.08,0:22:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's worse, you did it when her head\N was already full of her duties as director.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very talented.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.09,0:23:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you love her.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.72,0:23:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't say it like that... {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.51,0:23:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like she actually\N has a thing for you too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.97,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman's instinct.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.44,0:23:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true form.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.98,0:23:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some personal time today.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.28,0:23:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chie-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.45,0:23:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's only a rehearsal of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.16,0:23:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a man out of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.46,0:23:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no director and no camera in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.00,0:23:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.09,0:23:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chie-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.38,0:23:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We really shouldn't be doing this!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.76,0:23:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that kind of attitude that is putting Miwa-chan in a tough spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.93,0:23:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.05,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough talking for tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.88,0:23:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If... If you do that, I-I'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.33,0:24:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.89,0:24:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're big. Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.08,0:24:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hitting me all the way inside!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.10,0:24:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great... Just now...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.38,0:24:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.00,0:24:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's good!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.88,0:25:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fucking intense! \NSee? You {\i1}can{\i0} do it if you want to!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:02.22,0:25:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done! Here ya go.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:06.14,0:25:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Shinohara-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.81,0:25:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.23,0:25:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were great.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.64,0:25:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wrap! Good work, Shinohara-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.40,0:25:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Director!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.03,0:25:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.86,0:25:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get some good shots?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.32,0:25:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was good.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.95,0:25:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it wasn't awkward.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.45,0:25:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:28.58,0:25:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do some editing now,\N so I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.54,0:25:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Leaving already?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:34.33,0:25:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.21,0:25:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take some stills\N tomorrow at 9, thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.38,0:25:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.82,0:26:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And now I, Ujiki Masami, will be singing "Father and Son," with all due respect! {えー、僭越ながら私、氏木正美が『親子仁義』を歌わせていただきまーす！！}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.57,0:26:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, leave it be, Chief! \NThat's your eighth song tonight!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:13.91,0:26:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.58,0:26:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it sell well?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:18.63,0:26:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely. I think it will be\N one of the best in Chie's filmography.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.63,0:26:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you could look happier.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:26.51,0:26:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't feel too well. {lit: maybe a cold?}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.26,0:26:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.93,0:26:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ujitani-san, drink up!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.60,0:26:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make some noise tonight!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:35.39,0:26:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we got some great shots.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.52,0:26:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This will revive Apollo Productions for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:40.90,0:26:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast to Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.99,0:26:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try the other one! {lit: let's go next - no idea what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:52.53,0:26:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:54.12,0:26:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.83,0:26:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Scram!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:58.21,0:26:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:59.67,0:27:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.10,0:27:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time\N since I've run this much.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.64,0:27:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we lost the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:16.18,0:27:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is close to your apartment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.15,0:27:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go back to where we last saw them?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.98,0:27:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. I'm too drunk to walk any further.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:27.70,0:27:31.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,C-Could this be h-her way of seducing me?{false i-frame}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.99,0:27:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.29,0:27:35.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.25,0:27:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's heavy!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:41.88,0:27:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miwa-san, wake up, please?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:44.38,0:27:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.72,0:27:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Miwa-san? \NYour panties are showing!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:53.72,0:27:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.77,0:28:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:05.25,0:28:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault for showing me\N your colors like that! {lit: dazzling look}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.74,0:28:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want it!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:09.82,0:28:11.70,Overlap,,0,0,0,,How's that, you slut?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:11.70,0:28:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'ya like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.07,0:28:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking awesome! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:15.74,0:28:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I {\i1}wish{\i0} that would happen, \Nbut I lack the balls.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:33.09,0:28:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:39.77,0:28:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:51.40,0:28:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowlife! {/coward}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:52.91,0:28:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that for?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.95,0:28:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:55.87,0:28:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing my body when I was drunk!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:57.49,0:29:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:00.12,0:29:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:02.46,0:29:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you just listen\N to me for a moment?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:06.42,0:29:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do? H-Hit me?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:19.35,0:29:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin'.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:20.22,0:29:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You motherfucker.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:22.10,0:29:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Running off with Miwa-chan like that last night... {tonzura}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:25.31,0:29:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:26.19,0:29:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here she is.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:28.52,0:29:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They came to work together.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.74,0:29:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing on Koganei's face looks bad. {meaning "she slapped him good/seriously"}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:33.28,0:29:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miwa-chan's wearing\N the same clothes as yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:36.24,0:29:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:37.45,0:29:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you, Koganei!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:39.41,0:29:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you treat our poster girl like that! {pretty girl who attracts customers to come inside a shop - probably refers to their "interview"}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:41.83,0:29:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.62,0:29:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.87,0:29:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you, I didn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.99,0:29:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'd known you were gonna accuse me, I wish I had!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:49.25,0:29:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you would claim it so brazenly!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.05,0:29:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm convinced you did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:01.97,0:30:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koganei, are you guys still fighting?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:05.10,0:30:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.06,0:30:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really look like that much of a pervert? {like I'd do something perverted like that}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:09.11,0:30:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know. \NWhen I see your face on that screen...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.78,0:30:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But that was just acting!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.70,0:30:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.78,0:30:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, that's the face of someone\N who's cumming for real, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.08,0:30:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:20.24,0:30:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's scary to think that he also looked\N like that when he was on top of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.46,0:30:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just a minute, Director!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:27.33,0:30:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hear me out once, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:30.25,0:30:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:32.76,0:30:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, I just don't understand Miwa anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.93,0:30:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, it'll look like I really {\i1}did {\i0}violate her!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.64,0:30:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't do anything that night?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.22,0:30:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.77,0:30:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san simply jumped\N to the conclusion that I did!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.85,0:30:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And why didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:49.81,0:30:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You ask why I {\i1}didn't{\i0} violate her?\NBut that'd be so...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:53.36,0:30:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She does seem to hold some weird prejudices against men.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:56.45,0:30:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She slapped me once too.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:59.41,0:31:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't lose your spirit just yet. \NI'll smooth things over for ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.29,0:31:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:04.62,0:31:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, take care of this. \NYour senpai needs to go. {ja, kouhai ne}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.58,0:31:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy to!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.00,0:31:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.46,0:31:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.76,0:31:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you're up here, after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.89,0:31:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:25.02,0:31:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Still in the studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:27.06,0:31:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Koganei is still down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:32.61,0:31:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:33.65,0:31:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.23,0:31:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give Junpei-kun\N a message from me, please?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:37.65,0:31:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.49,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was still in my pantyhose, \Nand my body didn't feel any different.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.53,0:31:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm worried that\N I may have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:46.75,0:31:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. Right, I see. {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:48.00,0:31:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet for some reason, whenever I see Junpei-kun,\N I feel kind of awkward around him. {crabbily; unsociably}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:52.42,0:31:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, when I woke up, he was sleeping separately under just a sheet.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:56.46,0:31:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He acted like a gentleman. \NAnd in comparison, I'm just...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:59.68,0:32:01.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:01.18,0:32:04.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's already talking like he's her boyfriend! I gotta act now! {to go on about (one's love affairs); to speak proudly of (one's spouse, girlfriend, etc.); to speak fondly of​}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.10,0:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me! I was actually gonna keep quiet about this,
Dialogue: 10,0:32:08.63,0:32:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but seeing you like this, \NI can't hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:12.77,0:32:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Man, she was quite something!\NI still remember pounding her so hard."
Dialogue: 10,0:32:17.36,0:32:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be true!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:18.74,0:32:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:20.03,0:32:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:21.99,0:32:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you also enjoyed yourself a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:24.78,0:32:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:30.34,0:32:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's so dead! To think I was almost about to let it go! {あやうくうやむやになるところしだったわ！！！; }
Dialogue: 10,0:32:35.72,0:32:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You've done well by telling me!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:39.02,0:32:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\N I'm on your side, Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:43.35,0:32:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still in the studio, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:44.85,0:32:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.86,0:32:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I went a little too far?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:50.65,0:32:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I don't go this far, \NI won't stand a chance with her. {まあ、このぐらいこじらしてこないと、俺も調停の仕様がないからね。; very unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:56.12,0:32:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Senpai?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:58.16,0:33:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my friend, rejoice! \NI cleared up the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:01.62,0:33:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's actually kind of pissed now:
Dialogue: 10,0:33:03.75,0:33:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why did he take me back to his place \Nand not do anything to me?!"
Dialogue: 10,0:33:08.46,0:33:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what usually happens.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.38,0:33:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is shameful to reject\N the advances of a woman. {proverb: shameful is he who spurns a woman's invitation; not eating the meal set before him is a man's shame​}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.97,0:33:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa was actually after you, you dunce. {本当は監督回ってたんだぞバカ; unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:15.51,0:33:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But she was seriously mad, \Nand I don't quite understand why.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:19.14,0:33:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a nitwit.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:20.89,0:33:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With women, what they feel and what they show are two very different things.   {lit: feelings and attitude are opposite}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.14,0:33:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only acting embarrassed and mad. \NActually, she's feeling the opposite!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:27.86,0:33:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Women sure are complicated.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:33.49,0:33:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:36.95,0:33:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, um, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:38.66,0:33:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't really understand how you felt up to now.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:42.50,0:33:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you grin at me\N with that radiant smile?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:46.75,0:33:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You despicable man!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:48.14,0:33:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You even had the nerve to talk at length about how you took advantage of me, you swine!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:52.05,0:33:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I ever enjoy it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:54.05,0:33:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see your face ever again!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:56.76,0:34:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I don't really understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:00.97,0:34:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you still\N mean the opposite thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.56,0:34:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:04.93,0:34:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That you, like... That you actually want to sleep with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:12.61,0:34:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You dirty worm!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:16.68,0:34:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, I was so naive.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:18.49,0:34:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've known\N that men can't be trusted!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:21.37,0:34:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't get women!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:34.59,0:34:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you can buy our videos for cheap and get away with it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.93,0:34:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where did all this money come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:43.18,0:34:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Junpei and Director Miwa, \N{\i1}Love Juice Angel{\i0} was a big success.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.65,0:34:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the look \Non that scrooge's face? {takojiji = octopus grandpa - think octopus is there because he's a moneygrubber that is metaphorically trying to get his tentacles on everything he can reach, or maybe it's just a visual resemblance since koganei saw it too}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:01.41,0:35:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miwa-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:03.28,0:35:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That greedy old fart, the adult film industry loan shark, was just here. {/octopus}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:10.54,0:35:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Resignation?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:14.88,0:35:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:16.84,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting Apollo Productions today.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:20.38,0:35:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Did someone else poach you? {hiring from another company; recruitment; scouting; headhunting}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:22.89,0:35:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:23.76,0:35:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hesitant to bring personal feelings into the situation,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:26.58,0:35:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't continue working in a company with a man I can't forgive!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.77,0:35:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.73,0:35:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:35.26,0:35:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:35.86,0:35:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:36.94,0:35:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.65,0:35:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:39.24,0:35:40.78,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.08,0:35:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it. I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:53.92,0:35:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:55.50,0:35:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not before we both have some good old fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:57.55,0:35:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.17,0:36:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell not? \NWe've done it once before, didn't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:01.93,0:36:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even realize what you're saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:05.47,0:36:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What harm would it do \Nif we did it a couple times more?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:08.68,0:36:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:10.39,0:36:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:11.60,0:36:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you don't expect to win\N against a man like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:16.69,0:36:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:22.82,0:36:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just right.\NI'm starting to get a feel for it. {だいぶ感じが出て来たな。- ambiguous}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:26.87,0:36:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:28.66,0:36:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need lectures from you!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:30.54,0:36:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fuck your brains out! {/rape/violate}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:33.67,0:36:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:43.22,0:36:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san. Miwa-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:51.56,0:36:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Promise not to laugh? {lit: do not be amazed; be shocked}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:54.94,0:36:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels too miserable \Nfor me to remain hard. {lit: for myself, this is so pathetic, it [my dick] shrunk/squeezed itself in }
Dialogue: 10,0:36:58.44,0:37:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for holding you down.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:01.44,0:37:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a weak-willed guy like me \Ncould force a girl to have sex with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:06.57,0:37:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that night, seeing a woman \Nwho passed out drunk,
Dialogue: 10,0:37:10.41,0:37:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't force myself on her.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.77,0:37:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially on someone I love.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:15.00,0:37:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:16.21,0:37:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:18.63,0:37:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that felt refreshing!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:20.96,0:37:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can quit with no regrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:23.58,0:37:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility for scaring you like that \Nand quit this company tomorrow. {lit: for ending up in this form (as a monster who nearly raped you)}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:28.30,0:37:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you never \Nhave to see me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.52,0:37:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get to know you for long, \Nbut it was fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.49,0:37:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.43,0:37:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't quit!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.24,0:37:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.57,0:37:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:57.20,0:37:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miwa-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:58.61,0:37:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.85,0:38:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so blind! {obstinate; headstrong; perverse}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:01.80,0:38:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:05.20,0:38:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san, don't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:07.04,0:38:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll forgive me?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:08.29,0:38:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:25.79,0:38:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't quit! {no clue about this one or all the lines later}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:27.24,0:38:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:28.13,0:38:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:28.92,0:38:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget about us?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.03,0:38:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.80,0:38:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:32.01,0:38:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:32.93,0:38:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't push!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:22.75,0:42:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The future great filmmaker\N and the Apollo Productions newcomer,
Dialogue: 10,0:42:26.67,0:42:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Koganei Junpei, am ready for my next adventure!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:31.08,0:42:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this? The Apollo staff ends up
Dialogue: 10,0:42:34.01,0:42:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,working part-time at a host club \Nthat is struggling financially!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:44.02,0:42:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At the host club, Junpei-kun and others \Nmeet former great actress Mina Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:48.75,0:42:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he finds out that she's the mistress
Dialogue: 10,0:42:51.63,0:42:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of one of the world's wealthiest men, \Nthe president of a major consulting firm,
Dialogue: 10,0:42:54.59,0:42:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Junpei-kun just... {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:01.25,0:43:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stop here, my manhood will be ruined. {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:03.94,0:43:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the company and Miwa-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:06.09,0:43:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the time to throw myself into attack after attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:12.68,0:43:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected accident occurred just as filming began.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:16.63,0:43:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Director Shibuya collapsed in the middle of filming,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:20.13,0:43:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was suddenly appointed acting director.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:22.90,0:43:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the lead actress, Mikami Shoko, disliked her costar Takamura Toru,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:27.11,0:43:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and chose Koganei Junpei, \Nour Junpei-kun, for the main role!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:32.28,0:43:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa-san and I are fired up to complete this big movie!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:37.79,0:43:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it won't be long before \NI'm united with my beloved Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:10.41,0:44:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Good Time for an Adventure{\i0},\N episode two, is heating up for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:14.25,0:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On shelves soon. Stay tuned!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:28.09,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sexy Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.01,English,,0,0,0,,I met you at a party {by some miracle, I found a CD booklet with lyrics; Welcome My Sexy Cat Woh \NPartyで出逢った \NWelcome My Sweet Cat Woh \NJeans の妖精 \N「送らせてよ」と追いかけていった Motor Pool \Nサイド・シートに下心を乗せて \NWho/ だけどRadio から bad news ムードは sold out ジョークだけで\Nスゥイッチ・オン My heart, it's all right/\NWelcome My Sexy Cat Woh \N悪戯な光る瞳 \NWelcome My Sweet Cat Woh \N最高のタイプさ\Nとりとめのない やりとり交わす 湾岸 Road \N「12:00迄には送ってネ･･･」とささやく\N聞こえないフリで演じるぜ コメディー\N時計なんか外させたい\N矢継ぎ早の trick/trick/trick/trick/\NWelcome My Sexy Cat \Nまるで "Marie claire" のF.G. ページ \NWelcome My Sweet Cat Woh \NN*19 誘うぜ \NWho/time up 告げる時報 \N12:00まであと少しさ\Nスゥイッチ・オフ radio, it's all right}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.09,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sweet Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:37.04,English,,0,0,0,,A fairy in jeans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:42.64,English,,0,0,0,,I chased you to the motor pool, "Let me walk you home"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:48.33,English,,0,0,0,,Putting my ulterior motives on the side seat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:54.41,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa, but the radio is giving me bad news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:57.62,English,,0,0,0,,My mood is sold out, you're only joking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:01.06,English,,0,0,0,,Switch on my heart, it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:04.13,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sexy Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.05,English,,0,0,0,,Mischievous shining eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.09,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sweet Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.99,English,,0,0,0,,You're just my type
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:18.97,English,,0,0,0,,Rambling exchanges on the bay road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:24.25,English,,0,0,0,,"Please drop me off by 12:00," you whisper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:30.42,English,,0,0,0,,I pretend not to hear you, it's a comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.63,English,,0,0,0,,I want you to take off your watch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.82,English,,0,0,0,,You're like a machine gun, shooting tricks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.42,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sexy Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:42.95,English,,0,0,0,,It's like the F.G. page of "Marie Claire"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.16,English,,0,0,0,,Welcome My Sweet Cat wo-o-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.38,English,,0,0,0,,Number 19! I'm asking you out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:12.47,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa, time's up, the signal tells us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:15.65,English,,0,0,0,,It's just a little while longer until 12:00
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.97,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Switch off the radio, it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.55,0:38:53.89,English,,0,0,0,,Asphalt, the lonely building {same booklet; アスファルト 孤独のビルディング\N立ちすくむ 見慣れた都会\N時の流れに背中を押され\N生きるのも悪くはないさだけど\N\N作り笑いの パズリング・デイズ\N過ごしたくないだけなのさ\N\Nターミナル 仮面の群れを\N眺め疲れて コンコース歩いてみる\Nあと少しで P.M.5: 00 o'clock \Nworking time 脱け出せるけど\N\N出口は無いさ バズリング・テイズ\N独り 明日へ向かう \N\NJust a puzzle 合わす様に\Nリスキーなまま生きてくしかない \N"現実"に Never say no/\N\N作り笑いの バズリング・デイズ\N過したくないからさ \N\NIt's a puzzle 合わす様に\Nリスキーなまま生きてくしかない \N"現実"に Never say no/}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.10,0:39:00.99,English,,0,0,0,,Standing frozen in the familiar city
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.99,0:39:07.17,English,,0,0,0,,Pushed by the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.50,0:39:15.19,English,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.19,0:39:27.39,English,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to spend\N these puzzling days faking a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.85,0:39:34.61,English,,0,0,0,,Tired of looking at a crowd of masks
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.63,0:39:43.62,English,,0,0,0,,At the terminal, I walk down the concourse
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.45,0:39:47.66,English,,0,0,0,,It's almost
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.86,0:39:51.77,English,,0,0,0,,5 o'clock PM
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.37,0:39:57.16,English,,0,0,0,,I can escape from my working time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.92,0:40:01.82,English,,0,0,0,,But there's no way out of the puzzling days
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.82,0:40:08.58,English,,0,0,0,,I'm alone, heading toward tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.43,0:40:15.33,English,,0,0,0,,Just a puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.33,0:40:22.67,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.67,0:40:30.08,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.31,0:41:09.15,English,,0,0,0,,I don't want to spend\N these puzzling days faking a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.96,0:41:15.91,English,,0,0,0,,It's a puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.91,0:41:23.17,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.17,0:41:27.19,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.19,0:41:32.48,English,,0,0,0,,A puzzle that I have to piece together
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.48,0:41:39.99,English,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to live riskily
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.99,0:41:48.23,English,,0,0,0,,Never say no to reality!
